<measure quantity="1" unit="day">
<num value="1">一</num>日</measure>
<pc>，</pc>太祖語守信<pc>，</pc>將用<name key="梁周翰" type="givenName">周翰</name>掌誥<pc>，</pc>守信微露其言<pc>，</pc>
